{"type":"message","id":"bd004faf","parentId":"664af9b9","timestamp":"2026-04-25T09:32:23.334Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"It works! The GIMP CLI harness successfully created an 800x600 PNG image. Let me show the user the result.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n搞定了，GIMP CLI 已经装好并且实测成功 ✅\n\n**实测过程：**\n\n```bash\n# 1. 创建画布\ncli-anything-gimp project new --width 800 --height 600 --name test_canvas\n\n# 2. 添加图层\ncli-anything-gimp layer new --name Background\n\n# 3. 导出图片\ncli-anything-gimp export render /tmp/test_gimp_output.png\n```\n\n**结果：** `/tmp/test_gimp_output.png` 已成功生成，800×600 PNG ✅\n\n**它的能力范围：**\n\n| 模块 | 功能 |\n|------|------|\n| `project` | 新建/打开/保存项目 |\n| `layer` | 新建/删除/移动/合并/复制图层 |\n| `filter` | 滤镜管理（模糊、锐化等） |\n| `draw` | 绘图操作 |\n| `export` | 导出为 PNG/JPG/SVG 等 |\n| `media` | 导入图片文件 |\n| `session` | 状态查看、撤销/重做 |\n\n**使用方式：** 大多数命令需要进入 REPL 模式保持状态：\n```bash\ncli-anything-gimp repl\n```\n\n或者用管道输入：\n```bash\nprintf \"project new ...\\nlayer new ...\\nexport render ...\\nexit\\n\" | cli-anything-gimp repl\n```\n\n**评价：** 这个 harness 是 CLI-Anything 自动生成的，基础功能（创建项目、图层、导出）都跑通了。但复杂操作（滤镜参数、绘图笔刷等）可能需要 refine 来补充。要不要我再跑 refine 让它更强大？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"lm_studio","model":"qwen3.6-35b-a3b-q4_k_m","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777109529153,"responseId":"chatcmpl-l9jnp9k1av9xuvbmht5fh"}}
