{"type":"message","id":"0c42630b","parentId":"6d722bd2","timestamp":"2026-04-25T11:46:33.829Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user has Ollama installed but only cloud models, no local models. They want to install ComfyUI and are asking what model to download.\n\nLet me think about what to recommend:\n\n1. ComfyUI installation\n2. Model recommendations based on their use case (AI content creation, social media, etc.)\n\nFor ComfyUI models, the key ones are:\n- SDXL / SD3 / Flux models for image generation\n- Flux.1-dev or Flux.1-schnell are the current state-of-the-art for local generation\n- SDXL Turbo / SD 1.5 for faster but lower quality\n\n\n- Flux.1-schnell is the fastest option at 4 steps, while Flux.1-dev delivers higher quality but needs more steps and 47GB of VRAM. SD3.5-medium is another strong choice at 14GB with excellent quality. Given their RTX 2080 Ti with 8GB VRAM, I need to be realistic about what will actually run locally without hitting memory constraints.\n\nFor their hardware, SDXL or SD3.5-medium are the best fits since they'll stay within the 8GB limit, though they might need to use CPU offloading for Flux. I should recommend ComfyUI for flexibility, suggest a model based on their VRAM, and walk them through the installation process.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n先说结论：**你的 2080 Ti 4GB 显存是瓶颈**，得选对模型才能跑。\n\n**你的情况：** Ollama 目前只有云端模型，没有本地模型。\n\n---\n\n**ComfyUI 安装 + 模型推荐：**\n\n**推荐方案：SD3.5 Medium**\n- 画质好、速度不错\n- **显存需求约 6-8GB**，你的 2080 Ti 刚好能跑（可能需要 CPU offload）\n- 适合做封面图、社交媒体配图\n\n**备选：SDXL 系列**\n- 更成熟、资源多、插件多\n- 显存需求约 6-8GB\n- 画质稍逊 SD3.5，但生态丰富\n\n**不推荐：Flux.1-dev**\n- 需要 24GB+ 显存，你的卡跑不了\n- Flux.1-schnell 虽然快但画质一般\n\n---\n\n**安装步骤：**\n\n```bash\n# 1. 下载 ComfyUI\ncd /home/kensoulstar/Downloads\ngit clone https://github.com/comfyanonymous/ComfyUI.git\ncd ComfyUI\n\n# 2. 安装依赖\npip install -r requirements.txt\n\n# 3. 启动\npython main.py --listen 0.0.0.0\n```\n\n**模型下载：**\n```bash\ncd models/checkpoints\n# SD3.5 Medium (约 14GB)\nwget -O sd3.5_medium.safetensors https://huggingface.co/stabilityai/stable-diffusion-3.5-medium/resolve/main/sd3.5_medium.safetensors\n```\n\n---\n\n**要不要我先帮你装 ComfyUI？** 另外你 Ollama 要装本地模型吗？现在跑的全是云端模型，离线用不了。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"lm_studio","model":"qwen3.6-35b-a3b-q4_k_m","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777117570427,"responseId":"chatcmpl-qd614tbdysmfkgct4c3qme"}}
