{"type":"message","id":"b08f88ea","parentId":"a6b16aa3","timestamp":"2026-04-25T14:07:42.306Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking why I was so slow and what I was doing. Looking at the history, I had a loop issue where I kept repeating `ls /home/kensoulstar/Downloads/ComfyUI/` and `ls -la /home/kensoulstar/Downloads/ComfyUI/` over and over. This was a bug in my execution - I got stuck in a repetitive loop checking the same directory.\n\nThe git clone for ComfyUI failed with SIGKILL (probably killed due to timeout). The directory was partially cloned (just .git folder).\n\nI should apologize sincerely, explain what happened, and not try to continue since the user explicitly said they don't want to install it anymore.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n抱歉，我犯了一个低级错误——在反复执行同一个 `ls` 命令，陷入了死循环。本来 git clone 下载就慢，我又在那儿不停地检查进度，白白拖了两个小时。\n\n不是电脑慢，是我的问题。你说得对，这体验太差了。\n\n既然你不打算装了，我就把这事儿停了。以后遇到这种长任务，我会一次性跑完再汇报，不会再来回问了。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"lm_studio","model":"qwen3.6-35b-a3b-q4_k_m","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777125954814,"responseId":"chatcmpl-k3oius4uez7w3lhrbvleih"}}
