{"type":"message","id":"37d5fa49","parentId":"554c2ad1","timestamp":"2026-04-25T14:09:24.956Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking about what model to download for Ollama that can generate images. Let me think about what Ollama supports for image generation.\n\nOllama supports image generation models like:\n- **flux-schnell** - fast image generation, good quality\n- **flux-dev** - higher quality but slower\n- **stable-diffusion** models\n- **kolors** - Chinese AI company's model\n- **wan2.1** - image generation\n\nFor a 22GB modified 2080 Ti, flux-schnell would be the best choice.\n\nLet me check what's available on Ollama's library.\n\nActually, Ollama supports several image generation models:\n- `flux-schnell` - fast, good quality\n\n\n- `flux-dev` - higher quality\n- `kolors` - good for Chinese text\n- `wan2.1` - newer model\n\nFlux-schnell is the way to go here—it's fast enough for practical use and delivers solid quality. I'll give them a straightforward recommendation.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nOllama 支持的画图模型：\n\n**推荐：flux-schnell**\n```bash\nollama pull flux-schnell\n```\n- 4 步出图，速度快\n- 画质好，文字生成能力也不错\n- 你的 22GB 显存跑它绰绰有余\n\n**备选：flux-dev**（画质更好但更慢）\n```bash\nollama pull flux-dev\n```\n\n**不推荐：kolors**（偏中文，但画质不如 flux）\n\n---\n\n装好后我可以直接用命令行调它画图，比如：\n```bash\nollama run flux-schnell \"a cyberpunk city at night, neon lights, rain\"\n```\n\n要我现在帮你下吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"lm_studio","model":"qwen3.6-35b-a3b-q4_k_m","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777126133736,"responseId":"chatcmpl-5dxc4kzv0zgoc5x01g3ulo"}}
