{"type":"message","id":"d17b934d","parentId":"f8b17ae6","timestamp":"2026-04-25T14:18:10.360Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户问的是 ComfyUI 在 Ubuntu 上的安装过程，我直接给出清晰的步骤就好，不要啰嗦。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nComfyUI 在 Ubuntu 上的安装很简单：\n\n**1. 装 Python 依赖**\n```bash\nsudo apt update\nsudo apt install python3-pip python3-venv git -y\n```\n\n**2. 克隆 ComfyUI**\n```bash\ncd /home/kensoulstar\ngit clone https://github.com/comfyanonymous/ComfyUI.git\ncd ComfyUI\n```\n\n**3. 创建虚拟环境并安装**\n```bash\npython3 -m venv venv\nsource venv/bin/activate\npip install -r requirements.txt\n```\n\n**4. 启动**\n```bash\npython main.py --listen 0.0.0.0\n```\n\n启动后浏览器打开 `http://你的 IP:8188` 就能用。\n\n**5. 下载模型（放在 `models/checkpoints/` 下）**\n```bash\nmkdir -p models/checkpoints\ncd models/checkpoints\n\n# SD3.5 Medium（14GB，画质好）\nwget -O sd3.5_medium.safetensors https://huggingface.co/stabilityai/stable-diffusion-3.5-medium/resolve/main/sd3.5_medium.safetensors\n\n# 或者 Flux.1-schnell（23GB，画质更好）\nwget -O flux1-schnell.safetensors https://huggingface.co/black-forest-labs/FLUX.1-schnell/resolve/main/flux1-schnell.safetensors\n```\n\n**6. 常用插件（可选）**\n```bash\ncd custom_nodes\ngit clone https://github.com/comfyanonymous/ComfyUI_manager.git  # 插件管理\n```\n\n---\n\n**你的 22GB 显存跑 SD3.5 或 Flux 都够用。**\n\n要我现在帮你装吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"lm_studio","model":"qwen3.6-35b-a3b-q4_k_m","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777126657331,"responseId":"chatcmpl-porud46saas3wp8dt3iof"}}
