{"type":"message","id":"cdfe95d8","parentId":"f44a92e5","timestamp":"2026-04-25T19:06:30.717Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户在国内，访问 HuggingFace 会慢，需要推荐国内镜像站。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n对，抱歉。国内直连 HuggingFace 确实很慢，甚至可能连不上。\n\n推荐用 **HuggingFace Mirror**（魔搭社区）：\n\n```bash\ncd /home/kensoulstar/ComfyUI/models/checkpoints\nwget -O sd3.5_medium.safetensors https://modelscope.cn/models/lllyasviel/sd3.5_medium/resolve/main/sd3.5_medium.safetensors\n```\n\n或者如果你用 **ModelScope（魔搭）** 的 CLI：\n```bash\npip install modelscope\nmodelscope download --model stabilityai/stable-diffusion-3.5-medium --local_dir /home/kensoulstar/ComfyUI/models/checkpoints\n```\n\n魔搭通常比直连快很多。要我现在帮你下吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"lm_studio","model":"qwen3.6-35b-a3b-q4_k_m","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1777143974632,"responseId":"chatcmpl-jd52bb48x25amr1p5vkb3"}}
