{"type":"message","id":"079d98e6","parentId":"543cb4d8","timestamp":"2026-04-25T19:31:24.143Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"SD3.5 Medium has a different architecture - it uses three text encoders (clip_g, clip_l, t5xxl) that need to be loaded separately. I need to use the correct nodes for SD3.5.\n\nLet me look for the correct node types. SD3.5 Medium requires:\n- SD3TextEncoderLoader to load the text encoders\n- CLIPTextEncodeSD3 for encoding\n\nLet me try a different approach - use the SD3CheckpointLoader or load the encoders separately.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nSD3.5 的文本编码器需要单独加载。让我用正确的节点：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"203979953","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat << 'EOF' > /tmp/comfyui_sd35_prompt2.json\n{\n  \"prompt\": {\n    \"1\": {\n      \"class_type\": \"SD3CheckpointLoader\",\n      \"inputs\": {\n        \"config\": {},\n        \"dtype\": \"default\"\n      }\n    },\n    \"2\": {\n      \"class_type\": \"CheckpointLoaderSimple\",\n      \"inputs\": {\n        \"ckpt_name\": \"sd3.5_medium.safetensors\"\n      }\n    },\n    \"3\": {\n      \"class_type\": \"SD3TextEncoderLoader\",\n      \"inputs\": {\n        \"clip\": [\"2\", 1],\n        \"clip_g\": [\"2\", 1],\n        \"clip_l\": [\"2\", 1],\n        \"t5xxl\": [\"2\", 1],\n        \"empty_padding\": 0\n      }\n    },\n    \"4\": {\n      \"class_type\": \"CLIPTextEncodeSD3\",\n      \"inputs\": {\n        \"text\": \"a beautiful young woman with long black hair, smiling gently, soft lighting, elegant portrait, high quality, detailed face, photorealistic\",\n        \"clip_g\": [\"3\", 0],\n        \"clip_l\": [\"3\", 0],\n        \"t5xxl\": [\"3\", 0],\n        \"empty_padding\": 0\n      }\n    },\n    \"5\": {\n      \"class_type\": \"CLIPTextEncodeSD3\",\n      \"inputs\": {\n        \"text\": \"blurry, low quality, deformed, ugly, bad anatomy, watermark, text\",\n        \"clip_g\": [\"3\", 0],\n        \"clip_l\": [\"3\", 0],\n        \"t5xxl\": [\"3\", 0],\n        \"empty_padding\": 0\n      }\n    },\n    \"6\": {\n      \"class_type\": \"EmptyLatentImage\",\n      \"inputs\": {\n        \"width\": 512,\n        \"height\": 512,\n        \"batch_size\": 1\n      }\n    },\n    \"7\": {\n      \"class_type\": \"KSampler\",\n      \"inputs\": {\n        \"seed\": 12345,\n        \"steps\": 20,\n        \"cfg\": 8.0,\n        \"sampler_name\": \"euler\",\n        \"scheduler\": \"normal\",\n        \"denoise\": 1.0,\n        \"model\": [\"2\", 0],\n        \"positive\": [\"4\", 0],\n        \"negative\": [\"5\", 0],\n        \"latent_image\": [\"6\", 0]\n      }\n    },\n    \"8\": {\n      \"class_type\": \"VAEDecode\",\n      \"inputs\": {\n        \"samples\": [\"7\", 0],\n        \"vae\": [\"2\", 2]\n      }\n    },\n    \"9\": {\n      \"class_type\": \"SaveImage\",\n      \"inputs\": {\n        \"filename_prefix\": \"generated\",\n        \"images\": [\"8\", 0]\n      }\n    }\n  },\n  \"client_id\": \"comfyui-cli\"\n}\nEOF\ncurl -s -X POST http://localhost:8189/prompt -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" -d @/tmp/comfyui_sd35_prompt2.json 2>&1","timeout":30}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"lm_studio","model":"qwen3.6-35b-a3b-q4_k_m","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777145440239,"responseId":"chatcmpl-oentz7do12cofsxcsokqve"}}
