{"type":"message","id":"3b5578a4","parentId":"7da2dc12","timestamp":"2026-04-25T19:31:40.255Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"SD3CheckpointLoader 不是标准节点。让我查一下 ComfyUI 中 SD3.5 的正确加载方式。\n\nSD3.5 Medium 的文本编码器是分离的，需要分别加载 clip_g、clip_l、t5xxl。\n\n让我用更直接的方式 - 使用 SD3CheckpointLoader 的正确名称，或者使用 CheckpointLoaderSimple 并手动连接文本编码器。\n\n实际上，SD3.5 Medium 的 safetensors 文件包含所有必要的组件。\n\n问题在于 CheckpointLoaderSimple 输出的 clip 是 None，因为 SD3.5 使用多个文本编码器而不是单一的 CLIP。我需要找到正确的节点来加载这些编码器，或者使用 ComfyUI 提供的示例工作流来了解正确的连接方式。\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"891305387","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"find /home/kensoulstar/ComfyUI -name \"*sd3*\" -name \"*.json\" 2>/dev/null | head -5"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"lm_studio","model":"qwen3.6-35b-a3b-q4_k_m","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777145484380,"responseId":"chatcmpl-vk85sg3f6iiscor0bk4szj"}}
