{"type":"message","id":"bca3bbf3","parentId":"a9f0e21b","timestamp":"2026-04-25T19:37:16.830Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The issue is that the SD3.5 Medium checkpoint doesn't contain a valid CLIP/text encoder model. This is a known issue with SD3.5 - it uses a different architecture where the text encoders are separate from the checkpoint.\n\nLooking at the error: \"no CLIP/text encoder weights in checkpoint, the text encoder model will not be loaded.\"\n\nThis means the SD3.5 Medium checkpoint only contains the diffusion model (transformer), not the text encoders. I need to load the text encoders separately.\n\nLet me check if there's a separate text encoder model for SD3.5 Medium.\n\n\nThe SD3.5 Medium checkpoint is only the diffusion transformer, so I need to load the CLIP and T5 text encoders separately from the checkpoint directory. Looking at the directory structure, there should be text_encoder and text_encoder_2 folders containing the necessary encoder weights.\n\nI need to use the SD3TextEncoderLoader node to load these encoders, then pass them through CLIPTextEncodeSD3 for encoding. Let me check the ComfyUI documentation to understand the correct node structure for SD3.5.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n问题找到了！SD3.5 Medium 的 checkpoint 不包含文本编码器，需要单独加载。让我用正确的方式：\n\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"605551747","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls /home/kensoulstar/ComfyUI/models/checkpoints/text_encoders/ 2>/dev/null | head -5"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"lm_studio","model":"qwen3.6-35b-a3b-q4_k_m","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1777145796339,"responseId":"chatcmpl-gewhz5n2yrf5xnnfa9jlpe"}}
